SUMMARY:HUM — Investor Call
DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 Issuer: HUMANA INC (HUM)\nRoadshow: www.netroadshow.com | Entry Code: HUMA
 NA26 | Direct Link: www.netroadshow.com/nrs/home/#!/?show=07d48700\n\nDeal
  context:\nHumana Inc. has mandated BofA Securities\, Citigroup\, Goldman 
 Sachs\, Morgan Stanley\, and Wells Fargo Securities to host global fixed i
 ncome investor calls on Monday\, May 4th\, ahead of a potential issuance o
 f 10-year and 30-year fixed-rate Pre-Capitalized Trust Securities (P-CAPs)
  denominated in U.S. dollars via newly formed trusts ('Horseshoe Funding T
 rust I' and 'Horseshoe Funding Trust II'). The P-CAPs are expected to be o
 ffered under Rule 144A / Section 3(c)(7) and are anticipated to carry rati
 ngs of Baa2 (Negative) / BBB (Negative) / BBB- (Stable) from Moody's\, S&P
 \, and Fitch\, respectively\, in line with Humana's existing senior unsecu
 red notes. Goldman Sachs & Co. LLC is acting as Sole Structuring Advisor\,
  with Wells Fargo Securities coordinating marketing logistics\; the deal r
 emains subject to market conditions.
